  "detailed_description": "Being a planet in space can be very lonely, but fortunately there is life out there.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177260/extras/3ea3ee0ec3c291ec95e634cd488fb4e3.poster.avif?t=1688984684\" width=630 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177260/extras/3ea3ee0ec3c291ec95e634cd488fb4e3.webm?t=1688984684\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Search the corners of the universe for new friends, who will help you on your quest to become a happy little place to live. Manage your resources, and upgrade tools to advance.<br><br>Fight your way down deep, deep dungeons leading to the core of.. yourself? And gain the respect of mysterious space gods.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177260/extras/d7efdb5e1ddf7f81bd6f689d5ebbc46c.apng?t=1688984684\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177260/extras/d7efdb5e1ddf7f81bd6f689d5ebbc46c.poster.avif?t=1688984684\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=256 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>A space adventure in three chapters</strong> with a nice story to play through, full of adventure and colorful characters.<br><br><strong>Lots of varied gameplay</strong> like dungeons full of jerks, a ghastly stock exchange, deckbuilding battles, an evil quiz show, and more!<br><br><strong>Play how you want</strong> with support for both game controllers and mouse/keyboard.<br><br><strong>Extra super features</strong> like achievements to collect, more music, and new rewards for completing content.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177260/extras/8662a7be770d8d8c20ba19272ed30d54.apng?t=1688984684\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2177260/extras/8662a7be770d8d8c20ba19272ed30d54.poster.avif?t=1688984684\" class=\"bb_img\" width=620 height=256 /></picture></span>",
